      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum plasticity (bilinear isotropic hardening) for titanium alloy components; Hertzian contact with friction validated against independent screw-rod contact benchmarks.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V components modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening (E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, tangent modulus 1.8 GPa) consistent with published material characterization. Frictional contact (μ=0.2) validated against independent pin-on-block benchmarks. Model form judged adequate for the compression-bending loading regime."
