      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least two independent test conditions (e.g., loading rate, temperature, or fixture variation) to bound environmental sensitivity.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single loading rate (5 mm/min) and ambient temperature at both laboratories. While inter-laboratory variability provides some environmental bounding, only one formal test condition was evaluated. This factor is below the required level; the gap is noted as a limitation of the current validation dataset."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
