      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to test conditions; any deviations quantified and their effect on QoIs bounded.",
      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions (fixed lower fixture, displacement-controlled upper loading nose) replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry. Torque preload on pedicle screw set screws matched to test protocol (4 Nm). Deviations in polyaxial screw head seating angle (±2°) assessed via sensitivity study — QoI sensitivity < 1.5%."
    },
