      "rationale": "E/uval values of 1.31, 1.74, and 1.58 for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm respectively — all below 1.96. Percentage differences of 4.2%, 6.8%, and 5.1% — all below 10%. Both acceptance criteria satisfied for all three QoIs."
